Summary: Biochemical reaction from acenocoumarol to R-6-hydroxyacenocoumarol. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2C9, CYP1A2 or CYP2C19.
Biochemical reaction from acenocoumarol to R-7-hydroxyacenocoumarol. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2C19 or CYP2C9.
Biochemical reaction from acenocoumarol to S-7-hydroxyacenocoumarol. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2C18, CYP2C9 or CYP2C19.
Biochemical reaction from acenocoumarol to S-6-hydroxyacenocoumarol. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP2C9.
